### 6. CONSENT & AUDIT TRAIL

ATS-Toolkit implements a **mandatory consent tracking system**:
- Cryptographic consent hash (SHA256) generated before each scan
- Immutable blockchain-inspired audit log stored locally
- Users MUST provide valid consent verification to execute modules
- Logs serve as proof of authorization in case of legal scrutiny

**Consent Format:**
```
Target: [domain/IP/system]
Modules: [list of tools used]
Authorization: [contract reference, bug bounty program, ownership proof]
Timestamp: [ISO 8601 UTC]
Hash: [SHA256 cryptographic signature]
```

